name: small_scene(3D)
description:
This is a Lora model for generating small worlds. Its base model is watch__00500_V1, and although this Lora model works on other base models, the effect may be different.

Usage

These are my settings I always use it is recommended but not essential;

Steps: 25+

Sampler: Euler

CFG scale: 9 to 12

Weight: 0.5-0.8
